Description_lang: A fierce Druid of the Talon, Thisalee Crow suffers no patience for the Burning Legion or any other enemies.
AuraDescription_lang: Thisalee Crow is the most aggressive of the Druids of the Talon.

description_blz.zh_TW: 身為一位兇暴的猛禽德魯伊，黎沙莉‧烏鴉不管是面對燃燒軍團或是其他敵人，都沒有什麼耐心。
